Method described in the paper: [Searching for MobileNetV3](url_placeholder_2).

Hardswish is defined as:

\text{Hardswish}(x) = \begin{cases}
    0 & \text{if~} x \le -3, \\
    x & \text{if~} x \ge +3, \\
    x \cdot (x + 3) /6 & \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}

Shape:
    - Input: (*), where * means
